en: Formerly in Castellani, Paravey and Darthes collections. Found in 1865. Purchased, 1923.
The Group of Louvre F 110; ABV, 220, 35. Same graffito *S*O occurs on Louvre F 110 (Hoppin, Nikosthenes 33*).
